      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n<a href=\"url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly96aC53aWtpcGVkaWEub3JnL3poLXR3LyVFNSU5MCU4NCVFNSU5QiVCRCVFNSVBRSVCNiVFNSU5MiU4QyVFNSU5QyVCMCVFNSU4QyVCQSVFNyU5NCU5RiVFOCU4MiVCMiVFNyU4RSU4NyVFNSU4OCU5NyVFOCVBMSVBOA\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E5%90%84%E5%9B%BD%E5%AE%B6%E5%92%8C%E5%9C%B0%E5%8C%BA%E7%94%9F%E8%82%B2%E7%8E%87%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8\">2023年生育率</a><br/>\n<br/>\n臺灣1.09<br/>\n南韓1.11<br/>\n香港1.23<br/>\n日本1.39<br/>\n中國1.45 (用統計局給的數字，含金量不可謂極高)<br/>\n<br/>\n烏克蘭1.57<br/>\n<br/>\n感覺，戰爭，不如亞洲分房<br/>\n<blockquote>1.57跟16万肯定有一个是假的</blockquote><br/>\n我看看<br/>\n<blockquote>In total, 96,755 children were born in Ukraine between January and July 2023, whereas 135,079 were born during this period in 2021.<br/>\nAn average of 16,100 children are born per month in Ukraine in 2023, whereas prior to the full-scale invasion, an average of 21,000-23,000 newborns per month was recorded.</blockquote><br/>\n確實，原文是平均每個月16,100新生兒，到樓主這就變成2023年16萬新生兒，而且因為戰爭的緣故，數據僅統計1-7月。<br/>\n<br/>\n習近平的去英文化還蠻成功的？\t\t</div>",
